<section>
    <div class="container">

        <div class="d-flex flex-column justify-content-center align-items-center">
            <div class="GuideHeading text-center">At Stienhardt & Stones, we have rigorous quality control over the jewelry we make. Every piece is created and designed with great attention to detail and is measured by the highest standards. Therefore, to ensure your satisfaction and calmness, a detailed Manufacturing Warranty is attached to all pieces that protects from defects in the materials and workmanship.</div>
        </div>
        
    </div>
</section>


<!-- =====================================================================================================================================================
                                                                What Does the Manufacturing Warranty Cover?
=====================================================================================================================================================-->
<Section class="mrg_tb">
    <div class="container">

        <div class="row d-flex justify-content-center align-items-start align-items-xxl-center mx-0 cusMyMrg mrg_tb">
            
            <div class="col-12">

                <div class="headingBG  mb-3"><h2 class="heading text-start">What Does the Manufacturing Warranty Cover?</h2></div>
                
                <div class="aboutDesc">
                    The Manufacturing Warranty is valid for the defects in manufacturing, which include but are not limited to:
                    <ul class="m-0 pt-2">
                        <li>Design changes which may include prongs, or other settings that become undone</li><br>
                        <li>Material defects inclusive of gold, pleats of platinum, and silver.</li><br>
                        <li>Catches or any closing mechanism of necklaces, bangles, or earrings which are not in working condition</li><br>
                        <li>Resulting defects in the placement of stones.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                
            </div>
        </div>
        
    </div>
</Section>


<!-- =====================================================================================================================================================
                                                                What is Not Covered?
=====================================================================================================================================================-->
<Section class="mrg_tb">
    <div class="container">

        <div class="row d-flex justify-content-center align-items-start align-items-xxl-center mx-0 cusMyMrg mrg_tb">
            
            <div class="col-12">

                <div class="headingBG  mb-3"><h2 class="heading text-start">Eligible Items for Free Returns</h2></div>
                
                <div class="aboutDesc">
                    Even though we provide the best qualities possible, still, the warranty excludes the following.
                    <ul class="m-0 pt-2">
                        <li>The jewelry is damaged through wear and tear, intentional misuse, or undesired accidents.</li><br>
                        <li>Jewel stones lost due to carelessness in handling or poor care.</li><br>
                        <li>Work done on or the alteration of jewelry by non-approved jewelers.</li><br>
                        <li>Contact with abrasive substances which can erode metal or stones.</li><br>
                        <li>Misplacement or breaking of the ring.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                
            </div>
        </div>
        
    </div>
</Section>


<!-- =====================================================================================================================================================
                                                                Warranty Duration
=====================================================================================================================================================-->
<Section class="mrg_tb">
    <div class="container">

        <div class="row d-flex justify-content-center align-items-start align-items-xxl-center mx-0 cusMyMrg mrg_tb">
            
