                    The Manufacturing Warranty shall remain effective for twelve months from the purchase date. After this period, wherever possible, repairs and servicing shall be provided at a fixed charge.
                </div>
                
            </div>
        </div>
        
    </div>
</Section>



<!-- =====================================================================================================================================================
                                                                How to File a Warranty Claim
=====================================================================================================================================================-->
<section class="mrg_tb">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="headingBG  mb-3"><h2 class="heading text-start">How to File a Warranty Claim</h2></div>
        
        <div class="row d-flex justify-content-center">

            <div class="col-12 my-3">
                <div class="cusGuideBoxbrdr">
                    <div><strong class="f-20 cl-51">1. Inspect Your Jewelry</strong><br></div>
                    <div class="cl-51 pt-1">
                        <ul class="m-0 pt-2">
                            <li>When an issue that seems applicable under the warranty occurs, please reach out to our customer service agent right away.</li>   
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-12 my-3">
                <div class="cusGuideBoxbrdr">
                    <div><strong class="f-20 cl-51">2. Provide Proof of Purchase</strong><br></div>
                    <div class="cl-51 pt-1">
                        <ul class="m-0 pt-2">
                            <li>Make sure you have the original receipt or a proof of purchase. It is necessary to support your claim.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-12 my-3">
                <div class="cusGuideBoxbrdr">
                    <div><strong class="f-20 cl-51">3. Ship Your Jewelry to Us</strong><br></div>
                    <div class="cl-51 pt-1">
                        <ul class="m-0 pt-2">
                            <li>For qualified claims, we will send you complete steps to follow and an insured return interval.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-12 my-3">
                <div class="cusGuideBoxbrdr">
                    <div><strong class="f-20 cl-51">4. Expert Assessment and Resolution</strong><br></div>
                    <div class="cl-51 pt-1">
                        <ul class="m-0 pt-2">
                            <li>Our master jewelers shall regard your item, establish the problem and repair or replace the item when deemed appropriate.  Repairs are in most cases done within a period format of 10-14 business days depending upon how complex the issue is.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>

    </div>
</section>


